Hello,

My name is Trudy Brown, and I am writing regarding my order of Red Office
Chairs. (Order ID: ES-2012-TB2162545-41262)

The order was delivered to me damaged. Specifically, the right armrest on
one of the chairs was broken upon arrival. Due to this issue, I would like
to return the entire order, including all three chairs.

I kindly request a full refund of $1,105.55 to my original payment method.
I have attached a copy of my invoice for your reference.

Please let me know the next steps for initiating the return and processing
the refund. I look forward to your prompt assistance.Thank you for your
support.

Sincerely,
